                  student_mark[] = {student_1_mark, student_2_mark ............. student_120_mark}	
   Sample Output:	Average = 	(stu_1_mark + stu_2_mark + stu_3_mark ........stu_120_mark) / 120				
  (Hint: Use scanner statement and for loop)      */
  
  




